colonel abrams is major ! ! ! ! ! the best of colonel abrams is a bright collection of the artist 's dance classics and quiet storm masterpieces . with the cd opener `` specutlation '' you have a good sense of what is about to come . with such hits and garage classics like `` trapped '' , `` i 'm not gon na let '' and `` how soon we forget '' this makes the cd one of the best dance artist collections thus far . the best of also covers some of the quiet storms recording such as `` marquex '' and `` table for two '' with is also worth listening too and shows the diversity of the artist . many listeners may say `` hey he sounds like teddy pendergrass ! '' but trust me he has a style and voice all his own . trust me this is also a must have and you will get your moneys worth . buy it ! !